sequenceDiagram
    participant OCTT as OCTT (CS Simulator)
    participant CSMS

    Note over OCTT,CSMS: TC_D_01_CSMS - Send Local Authorization List - Full

    OCTT->>CSMS: BootNotificationRequest(reason=PowerUp)
    CSMS-->>OCTT: BootNotificationResponse(status=Accepted)

    OCTT->>CSMS: StatusNotificationRequest(connectorStatus=Available)
    CSMS-->>OCTT: StatusNotificationResponse()

    Note over CSMS: [Optional] CSMS queries current list version before sending
    CSMS->>OCTT: GetLocalListVersionRequest()
    OCTT-->>CSMS: GetLocalListVersionResponse(versionNumber=1)

    Note over CSMS: CSMS sends full local authorization list
    CSMS->>OCTT: SendLocalListRequest(updateType=Full, versionNumber>0, localAuthorizationList=[...])
    OCTT-->>CSMS: SendLocalListResponse(status=Accepted)

    Note over OCTT,CSMS: Validation: updateType=Full, versionNumber>0, localAuthorizationList non-empty
